title: Hour 1 -Kyler Murray's Huge Contract, Albert Breer
itunes:title: Hour 1 -Kyler Murray's Huge Contract, Albert Breer
description:
Dan weighs in on the Arizona Cardinals locking up QB Kyler Murray for big money, and talks to Albert Breer about that as well as the likely resolution to the NFL's investigation of Cleveland Browns QB Deshaun Watson.
